title: [Loelita's Outfitting]
[Loelita's General Store]
[Loelita's Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath an etched seaglass ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the glazed bamboo walls.  A wide knotted oak counter and an aqua-hued seaglass display sit in opposite corners while a braided seagrass rug rests on a glazed bamboo floor.
